description: Indulge in an incredibly delicious and refreshing experience that can only be provided by the famous Rita's Ice Truck!  Using real fruit and pure cane sugar, they are whipping up fresh batches of dozens of flavors of Italian ice, frozen custard, and Gelati (a scrumptious combination of both!)If you’re looking for the perfect frozen treats for your next big event, Rita’s is all you need.
name: Rita's Ice Truck
